{"tid":1849793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"就算成功三罷 都要留意執行方式","createTime":"2020-01-29T08:37:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T05:24:57.000Z","uid":331861,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8cc8939ca33d001a0398f03f474684f989bc30bc","tid":1849793,"uid":331861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:37:27.000Z","msg":"政府隨時利用三罷玩9市民<br />\n例如就算你話學校依家已經停咗課<br />\n教育局依然要學校搞啲咩網上學習<br />\n老師學生其實隨時仲忙過平時返學<br />\n<br />\n等同罷工一樣<br />\n而家勁多公司包括政府都home office<br />\n其實咁樣真係達唔到三罷目的<br />\n隨時仲衰過返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我唔知呢樣嘢同工會有冇關係</span><br />\n但我想講從今日開工嘅經驗可以睇到<br />\n如果到2月3號真係成功全港大三罷<br />\n大家<strong>一定唔可以</strong>俾公司迫到你home office<br />\n如果唔係根本違背三罷嘅原意<br />\n學生都一樣 如果唔係你屋企繼續忙着做功課<br />\n根本就會同場運動脫節<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6733fbb95cb7dcb040b84c99d7fce4f4df3e8b8a","tid":1849793,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:41:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Poor Man EMP</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://public.milcyber.org/activities/magazine/articles/2020/20200120-renda\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.milcyber.org%2Factivities%2Fmagazine%2Farticles%2F2020%2F20200120-renda&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Jsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=f0162ac9\" target=\"_blank\">https://public.milcyber.org/activities/magazine/articles/2020/20200120-renda</a>"},{"pid":"930079abfaf0d105eb77f240535e73e985b3e700","tid":1849793,"uid":24596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:46:23.000Z","msg":"係，林鄭陰招，等啲搖擺緊嘅唔知其他人有冇擺"},{"pid":"038574fd4793523cd6ce7e12de968a9c3cbe1e48","tid":1849793,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:50:06.000Z","msg":"請假當罷工，home office都可以當罷工"},{"pid":"ae7d9a51caf5ad01618b8a8f5d6026d59b60d3f7","tid":1849793,"uid":331861,"like":2,"dislike":0,"s